Generate Ideas Functionality:
==============================
✓ VERIFIED FUNCTIONAL

The Generate Ideas button:
- Located in Content Builder > Constraints panel (line 936-951)
- Properly connected to generateIdeas() function
- Disabled when no insights selected or loading
- Shows loading state with spinner when active
- Function uses correct string format: i.split('\n')[0]
- Successfully calls AI agent with AGENT_IDS.ideaGenerator
- Pre-populates draft with first idea's hook and concept
- Navigates to drafts screen on success
- Handles errors gracefully with console logging

Workflow:
1. User selects insights in Content Builder
2. User adjusts constraints (format, effort, tone)
3. User clicks "Generate Ideas" button
4. AI agent generates idea_cards
5. First idea pre-fills the draft
6. User automatically navigated to Drafts screen

